data.description: In a market of homes over $200 sqft, here is a home under $150 sqft. A definite fixer upper, just waiting on someone to invest the sweat equity to restore it to its former beauty. Large and spacious home with 4 bedrooms, 3 living areas and 2 dining areas. Could easily accommodate 2 primary bedrooms - one upstairs and one downstairs. Wood floors downstairs. Spacious laundry roo with sink.The kitchen and laundry room have granite counters. The neighborhood is in the heart of Allen - conveniently located near schools, shopping, restaurants, parks, and more and yet it is a quiet neighborhood with wonderful neighbors. See it for its possibilities.
